  "text": "Oh, please, I'm almost ready. Is there anything that we can do to make the instrument more comfortable? I am Ra. You are conscientious. Be careful only to adjust this instrument's upper appendages if its upper body is elevated. I am Ra. All is well. It is our joy to speak with you. We leave in the love and the light of the One Infinite Creator. Go forth, therefore, rejoicing in the power and the peace of the One Creator. Adonai.",
